track_notes: Park in the large CP on the West side of the pass.  Take the path that leaves the CP at the north end.  Turn immediately left and pick up the stone flagged path.  This follows a well thought out line that weaves a route up the steep slopes. It arrives onto the flat ground almost at the summit.

Plenty of free car parking opposite Kirkstone Pass Inn. Pass through small wooden gate at corner of car park and follow obvious path up to the summit. Some minor scrambling is required in places. Plenty of space for HF antennas and great views.
track_title: Red Screes from Kirkstone Pass Inn

track_notes: Total time (including ops): 1hr 35m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T2. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards.
